displayName.text: Third Avenue Pediatrics Care: Ghooi Ashok MD

adrFormatAddress: 2032 3rd Ave, New York, NY 10029-2802, USA

originalText.text: Love Dr. Ghooi and his staff. Everyone is serious about there job and pay attention to quality, this means alot when dealing with the importance of child health.  Some laughs and smiles and a home setting enviorment with many families waiting to see the doctor as well. The walk-in priviledge is appreciated as well. I have been with them since my son was 2 and he is 14 now. The location is a bit smaller on third but its clean and still with the same staff from years ago, that actually speaks volumes about the establishment when you have long time loyal employees as well.
